{"id":"21064","name":"슈룸 모험기","rarity":4,"path":"Elation","desc":"「마치슈룸, 파키 비경에 온 걸 환영해~♥~」\n「단슈룸, 그렇게 굳은 표정 짓지 말고 웃어봐!」\n「그레이슈룸, 벌써 이 대왕님의 매력에 푹 빠진 거야? 아주 좋아!」\n「그리고 꾸꾸 버섯——그래 너, 아주 맛있어 보이는걸~」\n어서 도망쳐, 인간의 욕망은 채울 수 없는 토끼굴이니까——\n이리 와, 웃어봐, 이 화려한 세계의 일원이 되는 거야——\n「당신만을 위한 프로그램에 오신 걸 환영합니다. 누구나 귀여운 스파키가 될 수 있어요!」","icon":"icon/light_cone/21064.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/21064.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/21064.png","ranks":{"id":"21064","skill":"난투","desc":"장착한 캐릭터의 환락도가 #1[i]% 증가한다. 장착한 캐릭터가 환락 스킬 발동 시, 모든 적이 받는 환락 피해가 #2[i]% 증가한다, 지속 시간: #3[i]턴","params":[[0.12,0.06,2],[0.14,0.07,2],[0.16,0.08,2],[0.18,0.09,2],[0.2,0.1,2]],"properties":[[{"type":"ElationDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.12}],[{"type":"ElationDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.14}],[{"type":"ElationDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.16}],[{"type":"ElationDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.18}],[{"type":"ElationDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.2}]]},"promotions":{"id":"21064","values":[{"hp":{"base":38.4,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":21.6,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":18,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":84.48,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":47.52,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":39.6,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":145.92,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":82.08,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":68.4,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":207.36,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":116.64,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":97.2,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":268.8,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":151.2,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":126,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":330.24,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":185.76,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":154.8,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":391.68,"step":5.76},"atk":{"base":220.32,"step":3.24},"def":{"base":183.6,"step":2.7}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":4000},{"id":"116001","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":8000},{"id":"110261","num":3},{"id":"116001","num":10}],[{"id":"2","num":16000},{"id":"110262","num":3},{"id":"116002","num":6}],[{"id":"2","num":40000},{"id":"110262","num":6},{"id":"116002","num":9}],[{"id":"2","num":80000},{"id":"110263","num":4},